quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  91,1,"Mi woo…óndarii na'ange e mbeeta mum."
  91,2,"Mi woo…óndirii lewru sundu rewii e henge."
  91,3,"Mi woo…óndirii √±alawma sombo hu√±ciima."
  91,4,"Mi woo…óndarii jehma si mbo arii e ni…ì…ìidde."
  91,5,"Mi woo…óndirii kammu e mahdi mammba."
  91,6,"Mi woo…óndirii leydi no ndi wertarii."
  91,7,"Mi woo…óndirii fittaandu e ko foocci ndu."
  91,8,"O …ìannginani ndu faajiraagal e kulol alla."
  91,9,"Malaama noon oon laa…ì…ìin…óo ndu."
  91,10,"Ko goongo perti oon mutnu…óo fittaandu mum e goopi."
  91,11,"Samuudinkoo…ìe …ìeen njeddiino nulaa…ìe …ìeen."
  91,12,"Tuma nde nelaa …ìur…óo hiiteede e mu' en."
  91,13,"Nelaa…óo Alla wi …óum ko ngeloobo njarla …óaleeba e njaram mabba."
  91,14,"∆Åe njeddi …óum …ìe mborii ba, joomiraawo ommbi e dow mu'en lepte sabu bakkatuuji mum en o hu…ìtadi …ìe lepte."
  91,15,"Te o hulaani battane mum."
